msgstr ""
"Ma yella aseqdac yerna izegrar-nniḍen, ad ttwakksen daɣen, ala ma yella yebda timeẓlit d yimeskaren-nniḍen. Ihi, aseqdac ad yettwakkes d ameskar. D imeskaren-nni ara iḥerzen timeẓlit n uzegrir."

